    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>This recipe takes around 5-10 min to prep, so get your casserole dish and all your ingredients ready, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Make sure your dish is oven-proof and safe to use on the hob. Don't have one? Start cooking in a large, wide-based pan then transfer to an oven-proof dish and cover tightly with foil</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sri-lankan-style-pineapple-cashew-and-coconut-curry/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>white long grain rice</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>with 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cover tightly with<strong> tin foil </strong>and put the dish in the oven for 30 min or until all the water is absorbed and the rice is cooked \u2013 this is your <strong>baked rice</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sri-lankan-style-pineapple-cashew-and-coconut-curry/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a <strong>hob-safe oven-proof casserole dish</strong> with a matching lid with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Drain your <strong>pineapple</strong> <strong>slices</strong> (save the juice!) and chop roughly</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sri-lankan-style-pineapple-cashew-and-coconut-curry/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the<strong> onion wedges</strong> and <strong>yellow mustard seeds </strong>with your <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>ground turmeric </strong>and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sri-lankan-style-pineapple-cashew-and-coconut-curry/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>butternut squash cubes </strong>and the<strong> chopped pineapple </strong>with the<strong> reserved pineapple juice</strong></p><p>Add your<strong> cashews</strong>, <strong>tamarind paste</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong>, <strong>creamed coconut </strong>and 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[225ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [300ml]</span><span class=\"text-purple\"> </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil, then cover with a lid and put the dish in the oven for 22 min or until the butternut squash is tender</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sri-lankan-style-pineapple-cashew-and-coconut-curry/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sri-lankan-style-pineapple-cashew-and-coconut-curry/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the butternut squash is tender, remove the dish from the oven and add your <strong>mangetout</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up, cover with a lid and return the dish to the oven for 2-3 min or until the mangetout is tender \u2013 this is your <strong>Sri Lankan-style pineapple, cashew & coconut curry</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sri-lankan-style-pineapple-cashew-and-coconut-curry/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Sri Lankan-style pineapple, cashew & coconut curry</strong> with the <strong>baked rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
